channel.title: New Song
channel.description:
So my Band, Dystopic Dawn, finally tried to upload a video. It isn´t perfect, far from it, but here it it is:
[url]https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&v=xx4RrbPqrIs&desktop_uri=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxx4RrbPqrIs%26feature%3Dyoutu.be[/url]
Any suggestions would be nice. Comments as well. This is only a demo, so just keep that in mind. When we eventually get a decent recording set-up and such, we hope to improve the quailty and produce a more diverse (instrumentally and vocally) song.
I would have put this in ShowOff, but it isn´t complete as of now. So instead, I put it here for your help and suggestions. We plan to release other songs, covers and originals. Thanks for your time.
